channel.title: How Do I Remove Crates? [PI]
channel.description:
Hey, I know I may sound stupid but please give me a chance im still a coder in learning. Basically I don't know how to remove crates and if there is a guide could anyone link me to it I have searched but can't find anything. If you don't understand what I mean by removing a crate, I mean you see in edgeville where the general store is located in RS there are some crates there and I would like to remove them.
Thanks, Mr Rushed
